    {
      "id": 4987,
      "type": "MarkdownNote",
      "pos": [
        -5512.201198732955,
        3088.92258533472
      ],
      "size": [
        420.45648419658187,
        580.7494272393578
      ],
      "flags": {
        "pinned": true
      },
      "order": 11,
      "mode": 0,
      "inputs": [],
      "outputs": [],
      "title": "Model Download Links",
      "properties": {},
      "widgets_values": [
        "# LTXV-2.3 Text/Image to Video\n---\n## GGUF Model\n**Choose based on your card size**  \n*Place in:* `models/unet`\n\n- [Distilled Models](https://huggingface.co/vantagewithai/LTX-2.3-GGUF/tree/main/distilled)\n\n\n## Text Encoder\n**Gemma 3 12B (FP4 mixed)**  \n*Place in:* `models/clip`\n\n- [gemma_3_12B_it_fp4_mixed.safetensors](https://huggingface.co/Comfy-Org/ltx-2/blob/main/split_files/text_encoders/gemma_3_12B_it_fp4_mixed.safetensors)\n\n\n## Dual CLIP Connector\n**LTX-2.3 Text Projection Connector (bf16)**  \n*Place in:* `models/text encoders`\n\n- [ltx-2.3_text_projection_bf16.safetensors](https://huggingface.co/Kijai/LTX2.3_comfy/blob/main/text_encoders/ltx-2.3_text_projection_bf16.safetensors)\n\n\n## Audio & Video VAE\n**LTX-2.3 VAE Files**  \n*Place in:* `models/vae`\n\n- [LTX-2.3 VAE Folder](https://huggingface.co/Kijai/LTX2.3_comfy/tree/main/vae)\n\n\n## Spatial Upscaler\n**LTX-2.3 Spatial Upscaler ×2 (v1.0)**  \n*Place in:* `models/latent_upscale_models`\n\n- [ltx-2.3-spatial-upscaler-x2-1.0.safetensors](https://huggingface.co/Lightricks/LTX-2.3/blob/main/ltx-2.3-spatial-upscaler-x2-1.0.safetensors)\n"
      ],
      "color": "#432",
      "bgcolor": "#653",
      "shape": 4
    },
