    {
      "id": 5009,
      "type": "MarkdownNote",
      "pos": [
        -5512.040813111917,
        3707.6085930398513
      ],
      "size": [
        417.46536390114875,
        583.2357514860737
      ],
      "flags": {
        "pinned": true
      },
      "order": 16,
      "mode": 0,
      "inputs": [],
      "outputs": [],
      "title": "Custom Nodes",
      "properties": {},
      "widgets_values": [
        "# Custom Nodes\n---\n## GGUF Node pack\n**GGUF Node pack required**  \n\n- [ComfyUI-GGUF](https://github.com/city96/ComfyUI-GGUF)\n\n## ComfyUI-GGUF\n**Install or update this node pack to get the Audio/Video VAE node**  \n\n- [ComfyUI-KJNodes](https://github.com/kijai/ComfyUI-KJNodes)\n\n## Power Lora Loader + Group Bypasser\n**Lora stack and bypass optional groups**  \n\n- [rgthree-comfy](https://github.com/rgthree/rgthree-comfy)"
      ],
      "color": "#432",
      "bgcolor": "#653"
    },
    {
      "id": 5019,
      "type": "Note",
      "pos": [
        -5081.258630571115,
        3471.087605570525
      ],
      "size": [
        375.2355280998672,
        820.0801805908668
      ],
      "flags": {
        "pinned": true
      },
      "order": 17,
      "mode": 0,
      "inputs": [],
      "outputs": [],
      "title": "How To Use",
      "properties": {},
      "widgets_values": [
        "==============================================================\nModels and Custom nodes\n==============================================================\n\nBe sure to download and install all ther required models and custom nodes. See the \"Model Download Links\" and \"Custom Nodes\" in the left panel.\n\n==============================================================\nText OR Image to Video\n==============================================================\n\nWant Text to Video? Set the \"T2V/I2V Bypass\" above to TRUE.\nWant Image to Video? Set the \"T2V/I2V Bypass\" above to FALSE.\n\n==============================================================\n1 OR 2 Sampler Stage Upscale Generation\n==============================================================\n\nIf you require upscale, enable \"Sampler Stage 2 - Upscale (Optional)\" above in the \"Fast Groups Bypasser (rgthree)\" node above.\n\nBe mindeful of the \"Video Settings\" resolution. For example x2 upscale of 640 x 640 will give you you 1280 x 1280. Higher resolutions DEMAND more memory.\n\n==============================================================\nPrompting\n==============================================================\n\n- Establish the shot. Use cinematography terms that match your preferred film genre. Include aspects like scale or specific category characteristics to further refine the style you’re looking for.\n\n- Set the scene. Describe lighting conditions, color palette, surface textures, and atmosphere to shape the mood.\n\n- Describe the action. Write the core action as a natural sequence, flowing from beginning to end.\n\n- Define your character(s). Include age, hairstyle, clothing, and distinguishing details. Express emotions through physical cues.\n\n- Identify camera movement(s). Specify when the view should shift and how. Including how subjects or objects appear after the camera motion gives the model a better idea of how to finish the motion.‍\n\n- Describe the audio. Use clear descriptions for ambient sounds, music, audio, and speech. For dialogue, place the text between quotation marks and (if required) mention the language and accent you would like the character to have."
      ],
      "color": "#223",
      "bgcolor": "#335"
    },
    {
